<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5351520>
    dc:description "Figs. 9–10. Ranatra species, left lateral view of head.9, R. parmata, specimen from Indonesia, Sumbawa (CL 2172). 10, R. thai, specimen from Thailand, Chiang Mai Prov. (CL 2201)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5351520/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5351524>
    dc:description "Figs. 11–18. Ranatra species, male left parameres, outer view with detail of distal hook. 11, 12, R. gracilis, specimen from Laos, Vientiane Prov. 13, 14, R. parmata, specimen from Indonesia, Sumbawa (CL 2172). 15, 16, R. spinifrons, specimen from Malaysia, Selangor. 17, 18, R. varipes, specimen from Laos, Khammouane Prov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5351524/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5351532>
    dc:description "Figs. 27–29. Ranatra species, forelegs. 27, R. longipes longipes, specimen from Singapore, Nee Soon.28, R. rafflesi, specimen from Singapore, Selatar Reservoir. 29, R. varipes, specimen from Laos, Khammouane Prov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5351532/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5351528>
    dc:description "Figs. 19–24. Ranatra species, male left parameres, outer view with detail of distal hook. 19, 20, R. longipes, specimen from Singapore, Nee Soon. 21, 22, R. thai, specimen from Thailand, Chiang Mai Prov. (CL 2201). 23, 24, R. rafflesi, specimen from Singapore, Selatar Reservoir." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5351528/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

